::CyberShark::

    He was glad that Battera would join him to get a bite. He started to make 
his was down to the cafeteria. On his way he noticed that doors were shut, he 
couldn't figure out why. Until he saw the computer in the cafeteria. It said 
that the Destrons have visitors and that Magmatron sealed all the doors 
leading to other parts of the ship so the visitors could only get to the 
Conference Room. Magmatron was still waiting for them.
    He got in line to get some food. "Hmmm....One energonburger and a 
McenergonFlurry (play on McFlurry)" He told the computer. His order was 
served hot and fresh without bot whipping towels at each other. (A problem at 
our local McDonald's (TM))
